<COREF ID="54" TYPE="IDENT">Grace Kuo</COREF> says the textile industry <COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">today</COREF> needs to take a lead from the electronics industry , and constantly strive for innovation : " What consumer <COREF ID="34" TYPE="IDENT">today</COREF> does n't already have a wardrobe full of clothes ?
