<TEXT PARTNO="004">
Flexibility v. perfectionism
However , <COREF ID="40" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="21" TYPE="IDENT">G - Fun Industrial Corporation</COREF> general manager Tsai Chiu - hsiung , who worked at <COREF ID="35" TYPE="IDENT">the CTI</COREF> for many years before setting up in business for <COREF ID="40" TYPE="IDENT">himself</COREF> in late 1998</COREF> , has had a different experience .
