Looking into the future , <COREF ID="48" TYPE="IDENT">Chang</COREF> hopes that as a key material , stainless steel fiber can have a " locomotive " effect , encouraging various industries in <COREF ID="30" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> to develop a range of different products .
